text: Reynoldsburg is an unincorporated community in Johnson County, Illinois, United States. The community is located at the intersection of Gum Springs Road and Reynoldsburg Road northeast of Vienna. Reynoldsburg had a post office from 1860 to 1879. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Johnson County, Illinois Category:Unincorporated communities in Illinois
